## ğŸš€ Quick Start

### Prerequisites
- Python 3.8 or higher
- pip package manager
- SQLite (included with Python)

### Installation

#### Method 1: From Source
```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/luxion.git
cd luxion

# Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Run the application
python luxion.py
